Package net.minecraftforge.event.level

Klasse ChunkWatchEvent.UnWatch

java.lang.Object
net.minecraftforge.eventbus.api.Event
net.minecraftforge.event.level.ChunkWatchEvent
net.minecraftforge.event.level.ChunkWatchEvent.UnWatch
Umschließende Klasse:
ChunkWatchEvent
public static class ChunkWatchEvent.UnWatch extends ChunkWatchEvent
This event is fired when server sends "forget chunk" packet to the ServerPlayer.

This event is not cancellable and does not have a result.

This event is fired on the main Forge event bus only on the logical server.
